Axiom atleastp_SNoS_ordsucc_omega_Power_omega: atleastp (SNoS_ (ordsucc omega)) (Power omega).

Axiom Repl_finite: forall f:set -> set, forall X, finite X -> finite {f x|x :e X}.

Axiom infinite_bigger: forall X c= omega, infinite X -> forall m :e omega, exists n :e X, m :e n.

Axiom equip_real_Power_omega: equip real (Power omega).

Axiom form100_22_real_uncountable_atleastp: ~atleastp real omega.

Axiom form100_22_real_uncountable_equip: ~equip real omega.

